snippet.title: ZooRacers July 2022 Beta V.0.6 Footage
snippet.description:
The video you are about to watch does not represent the final version of ZooRacers. You will see content that is in progress. All player abilities, design animation, map, and camera views are likely to change in some way before launch. This video is our attempt to provide a quick view of the ZooRacers open battle map.
Images courtesy of YggDrazil.

🎮 Official ZooRacers Teaser - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8E-1W6sCco0
